The final ceiling on expenditure for the European Parliamentâs budget will be set at first reading.
I would like to stress as important aspects of Parliamentâs work in 2006, first a better explanation to EU citizens of the European Parliamentâs work, placing particular emphasis, in this connection, on the role of the European Parliamentâs information offices in the EU Member States, and second, preparations by the European Parliament to play a larger role in the legislative sphere, as provided in the EU Constitutional Treaty.
