We expect further technical work to continue in the second half of this year, so that decisions of principle can be taken in the course of next year when the ratification of the Constitution is completed.
Parliament will be formally consulted on the proposal regarding the Minister at an appropriate stage, so tonightâs debate will be followed by others in which Parliament can amplify its views in the light of progress on which the House will be kept informed.
